_:Necab5c9c2c784f7092177624b846332a <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>On 1 April 2024, the entire business of RWM was transferred to LLWR, which was subsequently renamed Nuclear Waste Services Ltd (NWS Ltd).</p>\n\n<p>NWS Ltd is a wholly owned subsidiary division of the Nuclear Decommissioning Authority (NDA).</p>\n\n<p>LLWR was established to operate the Low Level Waste Repository site, owned by the NDA, and RWM was incorporated by the NDA in April 2014 for the purpose of delivering a Geological Disposal Facility (GDF) and providing solutions for the management of higher-activity radioactive waste. Following the merger, NWS continues to be responsible for these activities.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"board-of-directors\">Board of Directors</h2>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/liz-peace\">Liz Peace CBE, Chair of Nuclear Waste Services</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/david-prout\">Dr David Prout, Independent Non-Executive Director</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/mina-golshan\">Dr Mina Golshan, Independent Non-Executive Director</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/shrin-honap\">Shrinivas Honap, Independent Non-Executive Director</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/juliet-sotnick\">Juliet Sotnick, Independent Non-Executive Director</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/clive-nixon\">Clive Nixon, NDA Non-Executive Director</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/jacq-longrigg\">Jacq Longrigg, NDA Non-Executive Director</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/seth-kybird\">Seth Kybird, Chief Executive Officer</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/nigel-lister--2\">Nigel Lister, Environmental, Health, Safety, Security &amp; Quality (EHSSQ) Director</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/alex-de-keyser\">Alex de Keyser, Interim General Counsel and Company Secretary</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"executive-team\">Executive Team</h2>\n\n<p>Day-to-day management of NWS activities is delegated to the executive team. The executive team is accountable for implementing the strategy and operational plans approved by the NWS Board.</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/seth-kybird\">Seth Kybird, Chief Executive Officer</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/john-corderoy\">John Corderoy, Chief Technical Officer</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/chris-sly\">Chris Sly, Interim Chief Financial Officer</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/nigel-lister--2\">Nigel Lister, Environmental, Health, Safety, Security &amp; Quality (EHSSQ) Director</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/steve-glasson\">Steve Glasson, Commercial Functions Director</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/shameem-akhtar\">Shameem Akhtar, HR Director</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/mike-pigott\">Mike Pigott, Director of Sites and Operations</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/paul-tuohy\">Paul Tuohy, Interim Strategic Review Director</a></li>\n  <li>\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/vicky-bennett\">Vicky Bennett, General Counsel and Company Secretary</a> (on secondment)</li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/alex-de-keyser\">Alex de Keyser, Interim General Counsel and Company Secretary</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/simon-hughes--2\">Simon Hughes, GDF Executive Director</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
